Crane Co said shareholders at itsannual meeting approved a three-for-two stock split of itscommon to shareholders of record May seven. Crane said theadditional shares will be issued on or about May 21.    It said the number of common shares outstanding willincrease to 23.7 mln from 15.8 mln.    Crane also said shareholder's approved an increase in thecompany's common to 80 mln from 40 mln and authorized five mlnshares of preferred stock with a par value of one ct. Reuter&#3;